{"word":"Uriah","slug":"uriah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Uriah</b> <a href=\"#/H223\">H223</a> <br/> 1. One of David's mighty men:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=39'>2Sa 23:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=41'>1Ch 11:41</a> <br/> - David's adultery with the wife of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=5'>2Sa 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=5'>1Ki 15:5</a> <br/> - Summoned from seat of war by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=13'>2Sa 11:13</a> <br/> - Noble spirit of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=11'>2Sa 11:11</a> <br/> - David compasses the death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=25'>2Sa 11:25</a> <br/> - David marries the widow of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=27'>2Sa 11:27</a> <br/> - Called Urias<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=6'>Mat 1:6</a> <br/> 2. A priest:<br/> - The father of Meremoth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=33'>Ezr 8:33</a> <br/> - Called Urijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=4'>Neh 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=21'>Neh 3:21</a> <br/> 3. A priest<br/> Urijah, 3<br/> 4. A priest:<br/> - Witness to one of Isaiah's prophecies<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=8&verse=2'>Isa 8:2</a> <br/> - Probably identical with Urijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=10'>2Ki 16:10</a> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=10'>2Ki 16:10</a>Urijah, 1 "}]}